rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0001
rows.name: So, any plans for the rest of the day?

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0002
rows.name:
You've got your award ceremony
tomorrow. Best not to get carried
away.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0005
rows.name:
You can take a walk around town if
you like, but in all honesty, we'd be
better off standing by at the inn.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0006
rows.name:
Yes, we don't know when we might be
next called upon.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]So no one's in the mood to go out.
Well, I don't blame them.

rows.label: fev11_610_150_msg0008
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Am I the only one nervous about the
award ceremony? I don't even know
what to wear!
